"Please check your query and confirm that all template parameters are "
"surround by double braces, for example, \"{{ ds }}\". Then, try running your"
" query again."
msgstr "请检查查询并确认所有模板参数都用双大括号括起来，例如 \"{{ ds }}\"。然后，再次尝试运行查询"

