#: superset-frontend/src/dashboard/components/gridComponents/new/NewRow.tsx:33
msgid "Row"
msgstr "行"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/customControls.tsx:100
msgid "Series"
msgstr "系列"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/customControls.tsx:102
msgid "Calculate contribution per series or row"
msgstr "计算每个系列或总计的贡献"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/customControls.tsx:115
msgid "Aggregation Method"
msgstr "合计"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/customControls.tsx:123
msgid ""
"Method to compute the displayed value. \"Overall value\" calculates a single"
" metric across the entire filtered time period, ideal for non-additive "
"metrics like ratios, averages, or distinct counts. Other methods operate "
"over the time series data points."
msgstr "计算显示值的方法。\"总体值\"计算整个筛选时间段内的单一指标，适用于比率、平均值或去重计数等非累加性指标。其他方法则基于时间序列数据点进行计算。"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/customControls.tsx:139
