#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:175
msgid ""
"The time granularity for the visualization. Note that you can type and use "
"simple natural language as in `10 seconds`, `1 day` or `56 weeks`"
msgstr "可视化的时间粒度。请注意，您可以输入和使用简单的日期表达方式，如 `10 seconds`, `1 day` or `56 weeks`"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:199
msgid ""
"Select a time grain for the visualization. The grain is the time interval "
"represented by a single point on the chart."
msgstr "为可视化选择一个时间粒度。粒度是图表中单个点所代表的时间间隔。"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:216
msgid ""
"This control filters the whole chart based on the selected time range. All "
"relative times, e.g. \"Last month\", \"Last 7 days\", \"now\", etc. are "
"evaluated on the server using the server's local time (sans timezone). All "
"tooltips and placeholder times are expressed in UTC (sans timezone). The "
"timestamps are then evaluated by the database using the engine's local "
"timezone. Note one can explicitly set the timezone per the ISO 8601 format "
"if specifying either the start and/or end time."
msgstr ""
"此控件根据所选时间范围过滤整个图表。所有相对时间（例如\"上个月\"、\"过去7天\"、\"现在\"等）均使用服务器本地时间（不含时区）在服务器端进行评估。所有工具提示和占位时间均以UTC（不含时区）表示。随后，时间戳由数据库根据引擎的本地时区进行评估。请注意，如果指定开始时间和/或结束时间，可以按照ISO"
" 8601格式显式设置时区。"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:229
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-ag-grid-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:396
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-ag-grid-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:405
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:184
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:420
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:429
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/controls.tsx:375
msgid "Row limit"
msgstr "行限制"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:238
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-ag-grid-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:423
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:447
msgid ""
"Limits the number of the rows that are computed in the query that is the "
"source of the data used for this chart."
msgstr "限制了用于此图表的数据源查询中计算的行数。"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:245
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-ag-grid-table/src/AgGridTable/components/CustomHeader.tsx:210
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-ag-grid-table/src/AgGridTable/index.tsx:601
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/MixedTimeseries/controlPanel.tsx:109
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-pivot-table/src/plugin/controlPanel.tsx:153
msgid "Sort Descending"
msgstr "降序"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:247
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-ag-grid-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:348
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-table/src/controlPanel.tsx:372
msgid ""
"If enabled, this control sorts the results/values descending, otherwise it "
"sorts the results ascending."
msgstr "如果启用，此控件将对结果/值进行降序排序，否则将进行升序排序。"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:260
#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:276
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/controls.tsx:385
msgid "Series limit"
msgstr "系列限制"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:265
#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:280
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/controls.tsx:389
msgid ""
"Limits the number of series that get displayed. A joined subquery (or an "
"extra phase where subqueries are not supported) is applied to limit the "
"number of series that get fetched and rendered. This feature is useful when "
"grouping by high cardinality column(s) though does increase the query "
"complexity and cost."
msgstr ""
"限制显示的系列数。应用联接的子查询(或不支持子查询的额外阶段)来限制获取和呈现的序列数量。此功能在按高基数列分组时很有用，但会增加查询的复杂性和成本。"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:291
msgid "Group remaining as \"Others\""
msgstr "将剩余分组保留为“其他”"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:293
msgid ""
"Groups remaining series into an \"Others\" category when series limit is "
"reached. This prevents incomplete time series data from being displayed."
msgstr "当达到系列数量限制时，将剩余系列归入\"其他\"类别。这可以防止显示不完整的时间序列数据。"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:305
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:160
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/controls.tsx:457
msgid "Y Axis Format"
msgstr "Y 轴格式化"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:326
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/components/controls/ColumnConfigControl/constants.tsx:169
msgid "Currency format"
msgstr "货币格式"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:328
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/components/controls/ColumnConfigControl/constants.tsx:170
msgid ""
"Format metrics or columns with currency symbols as prefixes or suffixes. "
"Choose a symbol manually or use 'Auto-detect' to apply the correct symbol "
"based on the dataset's currency code column. When multiple currencies are "
"present, formatting falls back to neutral numbers."
msgstr ""
"使用货币符号作为前缀或后缀来格式化指标或列。手动选择一个符号，或使用\"自动检测\"根据数据集的货币代码列应用正确的符号。当存在多种货币时，格式化将回退为中性数字。"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:339
msgid "Time format"
msgstr "时间格式"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:354
msgid "X Axis Number Format"
msgstr "X 轴格式化"

