msgstr "绘制图表的配色方案"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:386
msgid "Match time shift color with original series"
msgstr "匹配时间偏移颜色与原始系列"

#: superset-frontend/packages/superset-ui-chart-controls/src/shared-controls/sharedControls.tsx:389
msgid ""
"When unchecked, colors from the selected color scheme will be used for time "
"shifted series"
msgstr "取消选中时，将使用所选配色方案中的颜色来表示时间偏移序列。"

