msgid "Column"
msgstr "列"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:50
msgid "Numeric column used to calculate the histogram."
msgstr "选择数值列来绘制直方图"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:69
#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:73
msgid "Bins"
msgstr "处于"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:72
msgid "The number of bins for the histogram"
msgstr "选择直方图的分箱数量"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:82
msgid "Normalize"
msgstr "标准化"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:83
msgid ""
"\n"
"                The normalize option transforms the histogram values into proportions or\n"
"                probabilities by dividing each bin's count by the total count of data points.\n"
"                This normalization process ensures that the resulting values sum up to 1,\n"
"                enabling a relative comparison of the data's distribution and providing a\n"
"                clearer understanding of the proportion of data points within each bin."
msgstr ""
"标准化选项通过将每个柱的计数除以数据点总数，将直方图值转换为比例或概率。\n"
"此标准化过程确保结果值之和为1，\n"
"从而能够对数据分布进行相对比较，并更清晰地理解每个柱内数据点的比例。"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:98
msgid "Cumulative"
msgstr "累计"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/controlPanel.tsx:99
msgid ""
"\n"
"                The cumulative option allows you to see how your data accumulates over different\n"
"                values. When enabled, the histogram bars represent the running total of frequencies\n"
"                up to each bin. This helps you understand how likely it is to encounter values\n"
"                below a certain point. Keep in mind that enabling cumulative doesn't change your\n"
"                original data, it just changes the way the histogram is displayed."
msgstr ""
"累积选项让您能够查看数据在不同值上的累积情况。启用后，直方图的柱状条将表示每个区间之前的频率累计总数。这有助于您了解遇到低于某个特定值的可能性。请注意，启用累积功能不会改变原始数据，仅会改变直方图的显示方式。"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/index.ts:56
msgid ""
"The histogram chart displays the distribution of a dataset by\n"
"          representing the frequency or count of values within different ranges or bins.\n"
"          It helps visualize patterns, clusters, and outliers in the data and provides\n"
"          insights into its shape, central tendency, and spread."
msgstr ""
"直方图通过展示不同范围或区间内值的频率或计数，\n"
"          来呈现数据集的分布情况。\n"
"          它有助于可视化数据中的模式、聚类和异常值，并提供\n"
"          关于数据形态、集中趋势和离散程度的洞察。"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Histogram/index.ts:66
msgid "Histogram"
msgstr "直方图"

