msgstr ""
"按此控件中指定的类别分解系列。\n"
"      这可以帮助观众理解每个类别如何影响整体数值。"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Waterfall/index.ts:58
msgid ""
"A waterfall chart is a form of data visualization that helps in understanding\n"
"          the cumulative effect of sequentially introduced positive or negative values.\n"
"          These intermediate values can either be time based or category based."
msgstr ""
"瀑布图是一种数据可视化形式，有助于理解\n"
"          按顺序引入的正值或负值的累积效应。\n"
"          这些中间值可以基于时间或基于类别。"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-echarts/src/Waterfall/index.ts:68
msgid "Waterfall Chart"
msgstr "瀑布图"

