"The colors of this chart might be overridden by custom label colors of the related dashboard.\n"
"    Check the JSON metadata in the Advanced settings."
msgstr ""
"此配色方案正被自定义标签颜色覆盖。\n"
"请在高级设置中检查 JSON 元数据。"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-word-cloud/src/plugin/controls/ColorSchemeControl/index.tsx:77
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/components/controls/ColorSchemeControl/index.tsx:76
