"The color scheme is determined by the related dashboard.\n"
"        Edit the color scheme in the dashboard properties."
msgstr "配色方案由相关的看板决定。在看板属性中编辑配色方案"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-word-cloud/src/plugin/controls/ColorSchemeControl/index.tsx:82
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/components/controls/ColorSchemeControl/index.tsx:81
