"You are viewing this chart in a dashboard context with labels shared across multiple charts.\n"
"        The color scheme selection is disabled."
msgstr ""
"您正在仪表盘上下文中查看此图表，标签与多个图表共享。\n"
"        颜色方案选择已禁用。"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/plugin-chart-word-cloud/src/plugin/controls/ColorSchemeControl/index.tsx:87
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/components/controls/ColorSchemeControl/index.tsx:86
