"You are viewing this chart in the context of a dashboard that is directly affecting its colors.\n"
"        To edit the color scheme, open this chart outside of the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"您正在查看的图表位于一个直接影响其颜色的仪表板上下文中。\n"
"        要编辑配色方案，请在仪表板外打开此图表。"

