#: superset-frontend/plugins/preset-chart-deckgl/src/Multi/controlPanel.ts:46
msgid "deck.gl layers (charts)"
msgstr "Deck.gl - 图表"

#: superset-frontend/plugins/preset-chart-deckgl/src/Multi/controlPanel.ts:49
msgid ""
"Select layers in the order you want them stacked. First selected appears at "
"the bottom.Layers let you combine multiple visualizations on one map. Each "
"layer is a saved deck.gl chart (like scatter plots, polygons, or arcs) that "
"displays different data or insights. Stack them to reveal patterns and "
"relationships across your data."
msgstr ""
"按您想要的堆叠顺序选择图层。第一个选中的图层将显示在底部。图层让您可以在一个地图上组合多个可视化效果。每个图层都是一个已保存的deck.gl图表（如散点图、多边形或弧线），用于显示不同的数据或见解。将它们堆叠起来，以揭示数据中的模式和关系。"

