msgid "Basic"
msgstr "基础"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1572
msgid "Default URL"
msgstr "默认URL"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1575
msgid ""
"Default URL to redirect to when accessing from the dataset list page. "
"Accepts relative URLs such as"
msgstr "从数据集列表页面访问时默认重定向的URL。支持相对URL，例如"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1588
msgid "Autocomplete filters"
msgstr "自适配过滤条件"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1589
msgid "Whether to populate autocomplete filters options"
msgstr "是否填充自适配过滤条件选项"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1595
msgid "Autocomplete query predicate"
msgstr "自动补全查询谓词"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1596
msgid ""
"When using \"Autocomplete filters\", this can be used to improve performance"
" of the query fetching the values. Use this option to apply a predicate "
"(WHERE clause) to the query selecting the distinct values from the table. "
"Typically the intent would be to limit the scan by applying a relative time "
"filter on a partitioned or indexed time-related field."
msgstr ""
"当使用 \"自适配过滤条件\" "
"时，这可以用来提高获取查询数据的性能。使用此选项可将谓词（WHERE子句）应用于从表中进行选择不同值的查询。通常，这样做的目的是通过对分区或索引的相关时间字段配置相对应的过滤时间来限制扫描。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1616
msgid "Extra"
msgstr "扩展"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1617
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Extra data to specify table metadata. Currently supports metadata of the "
"format: `{ \"certification\": { \"certified_by\": \"Data Platform Team\", "
"\"details\": \"This table is the source of truth.\" }, \"warning_markdown\":"
" \"This is a warning.\" }`."
msgstr ""
"指定表元数据的额外内容。目前支持的认证数据格式为：`{ \"certification\": { \"certified_by\": \"Data "
"Platform Team\", \"details\": \"This table is the source of truth.\" } }`."

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1653
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/components/PropertiesModal/index.tsx:445
#: superset-frontend/src/explore/components/PropertiesModal/index.tsx:459
#: superset-frontend/src/features/semanticViews/SemanticViewEditModal.tsx:194
msgid "Cache timeout"
msgstr "缓存时间"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1654
msgid ""
"The duration of time in seconds before the cache is invalidated. Set to -1 "
"to bypass the cache."
msgstr "缓存失效前的持续时间（以秒为单位）"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1661
msgid "Hours offset"
msgstr "小时偏移"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1663
msgid ""
"The number of hours, negative or positive, to shift the time column. This "
"can be used to move UTC time to local time."
msgstr "用于移动时间列的小时数（负数或正数）。这可用于将UTC时间移动到本地时间"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1671
msgid ""
"A set of parameters that become available in the query using Jinja "
"templating syntax"
msgstr "在查询中可用的一组参数使用JINJA模板语法"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1680
msgid "Normalize column names"
msgstr "标准化列名称"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1681
msgid ""
"Allow column names to be changed to case insensitive format, if supported "
"(e.g. Oracle, Snowflake)."
msgstr "如果数据库支持（例如 Oracle、Snowflake 等），允许将列名更改为不区分大小写的格式。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1689
msgid "Always filter main datetime column"
msgstr "主日期列"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1690
msgid ""
"When the secondary temporal columns are filtered, apply the same filter to "
"the main datetime column."
msgstr "当对次要时间列进行筛选时，将相同的筛选条件应用到主日期时间列。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1712
msgid "<new spatial>"
msgstr "新空间"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1713
msgid "<no type>"
msgstr "无类型"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1765
msgid "We are working on your query"
msgstr "为您的查询设置标签"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1783
msgid "Open in SQL lab"
msgstr "在 SQL 工具箱中打开"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1795
msgid "Error executing query. "
msgstr "已执行查询"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1797
msgid " to check for details."
msgstr "查看详情。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1832
msgid "Click the lock to make changes."
msgstr "单击锁以进行更改。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1835
msgid "Click the lock to prevent further changes."
msgstr "单击锁定以防止进一步更改。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1923
msgid ""
"When specifying SQL, the datasource acts as a view. Superset will use this "
"statement as a subquery while grouping and filtering on the generated parent"
" queries.If changes are made to your SQL query, columns in your dataset will"
" be synced when saving the dataset."
msgstr "指定SQL时，数据源会充当视图。在对生成的父查询进行分组和筛选时，系统将使用此语句作为子查询。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1939
#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1962
msgid "Format SQL query"
msgstr "格式化SQL"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:1989
msgid "Open SQL Lab in a new tab"
msgstr "在新选项卡中运行查询"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:2021
msgid "In this view you can preview the first 25 rows. "
msgstr "在此视图中，您可以预览前25行。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:2032
msgid " to see details."
msgstr "查看查询详情"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:2115
msgid ""
"The pointer to a physical table (or view). Keep in mind that the chart is "
"associated to this Superset logical table, and this logical table points the"
" physical table referenced here."
msgstr "指向实体表（或视图）的指针。请记住，图表将与此逻辑表相关联，并且此逻辑表指向此处引用的实体表。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:2155
msgid "Search metrics by key or label"
msgstr "按键或标签搜索指标"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:2167
msgid "Metric Key"
msgstr "指标"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:2172
msgid ""
"This field is used as a unique identifier to attach the metric to charts. It"
" is also used as the alias in the SQL query."
msgstr "此字段用作将指标附加到图表的唯一标识符。它也用作SQL查询中的别名。"

#: superset-frontend/src/components/Datasource/components/DatasourceEditor/DatasourceEditor.tsx:2211
