#: superset-frontend/src/dashboard/components/nativeFilters/FiltersConfigModal/FiltersConfigForm/FiltersConfigForm.tsx:1187
msgid ""
"Add filter clauses to control the filter's source query,\n"
"                    though only in the context of the autocomplete i.e., these conditions\n"
"                    do not impact how the filter is applied to the dashboard. This is useful\n"
"                    when you want to improve the query's performance by only scanning a subset\n"
"                    of the underlying data or limit the available values displayed in the filter."
msgstr ""
"为控制筛选器的源查询添加筛选条件，但这只限于自动完成的上下文，即这些条件不会影响筛选器在仪表板上的应用方式。当你希望通过只扫描底层数据的一个子集来提高查询性能，或者限制筛选器中显示的可用值范围时，这一点特别有用。"

